nda 都要見？"},{"pid":"e16d2912f8ce2792ade2e1e7a881b547a4cfdbcd","tid":2308501,"uid":144692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"返工想辭職 辭完職想返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生"},{"pid":"401cd81f76e1936e9a5c1d845eeedf5202df735c","tid":2308501,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"攪抄得咗開心<br />\n呢D唔係預咗既咩"},{"pid":"349962277925055efb06bf59da46c14fc554b3e6","tid":2308501,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"你姓黎？"},{"pid":"a78b102454474db71cf7d174fc643a924c7b68e1","tid":2308501,"uid":357591,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"2c4da0974fe1b430a909b73106ba4b3ac66abb86","tid":2308501,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"頭一星期幾正 日日打機，煲劇，悶悶地又打下J。<br />\n第二個星期係屋企已經開始悶，出街飲早/下午茶，唔駛同人迫好爽。<br />\n第三星期開始揾下工，鳩send幾十份，低技術工種，但0回覆。<br />\n今個星期開始覺得好灰，唯有揾兼職。一陣去尖咀見foodpanda <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"大把人失業啦<br />\n<br />\n我果位朋友由舊年7月一直失業至今<br />\n差唔多一年半了 （唔知仲可以撐幾耐）<br />\n<br />\n有位做工程的，2個月前被炒魷魚<br />\n一時睇唔開就跳樓，走左了<br />\n<br />\n另外幾位第1，2季失業的朋友，<br />\n暫時仍然係得一個搵到工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a37a916633ad41c873fb1c92c7f321d129772f3","tid":2308501,"uid":162567,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2c4da0974fe1b430a909b73106ba4b3ac66abb86","tid":2308501,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"頭一星期幾正 日日打機，煲劇，悶悶地又打下J。<br />\n第二個星期係屋企已經開始悶，出街飲早/下午茶，唔駛同人迫好爽。<br />\n第三星期開始揾下工，鳩send幾十份，低技術工種，但0回覆。<br />\n今個星期開始覺得好灰，唯有揾兼職。一陣去尖咀見foodpanda <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈"},{"pid":"b723571bdcc5ef4e8166b2d5d29ffbfbbd2b8cfb","tid":2308501,"uid":275498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"> 驚閪埋  被人炒左 咪方便你地排隊買樓囉</span></strong>"},{"pid":"77e8dab7a9e4c17208204307dc425822cb74c000","tid":2308501,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e9499bd25d132becb7471c51405508b16a90d1","tid":2308501,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"3個幾月無工返...而家狂搵兼職"},{"pid":"9c592eddedcc1b9f4f3a5fc69a5b6b5162348366","tid":2308501,"uid":155278,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02d83251bbe3756957e2ae5ee0ccf45332d10517","tid":2308501,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6e9499bd25d132becb7471c51405508b16a90d1","tid":2308501,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"3個幾月無工返...而家狂搵兼職"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"邊度多slash搵"},{"pid":"ffe3d2d348c107083448564eeacc0f2233796ef4","tid":2308501,"uid":114701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02d83251bbe3756957e2ae5ee0ccf45332d10517","tid":2308501,"uid":12437